    <div class="characters-container">
        <h2>Meet the Characters</h2> <!-- Changed <h1> to <h2> inside the container -->

        <div class="characters-list">
            <!-- Elliott -->
            <div class="character-card">
                <h3>Elliott</h3>
                <p>Elliott is a reserved individual who values meaningful invitations and thoughtful help. However, he strongly dislikes compliments, finding them insincere.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Rudra -->
            <div class="character-card">
                <h3>Rudra</h3>
                <p>Rudra is a dependable and helpful person who thrives on assisting others. Invitations are not his thing, and he only mildly appreciates compliments.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Ahmet -->
            <div class="character-card">
                <h3>Ahmet</h3>
                <p>Ahmet is a social butterfly who enjoys compliments and invitations. However, he struggles with offering or receiving help, finding it overwhelming.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Luna -->
            <div class="character-card">
                <h3>Luna</h3>
                <p>Luna is a lively and outgoing person who loves being invited to events. Compliments, however, make her uncomfortable, and she prefers minimal help.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Maya -->
            <div class="character-card">
                <h3>Maya</h3>
                <p>Maya is a thoughtful and caring individual who values help and compliments. Invitations, however, are not her favorite thing.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Jamal -->
            <div class="character-card">
                <h3>Jamal</h3>
                <p>Jamal is a charismatic and confident person who enjoys compliments and invitations. However, he dislikes being asked for or offering help.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
